{
  "id": "adv_event_2403_01_05_02",
  "title": "サニーピース\n＆みんな",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――全国ツアーが終わって、数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days after the nationwide tour.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.8222773952,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1915.6127554
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "ただいま～\n……あら？　みんなで集まって何をしてるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm home~.\n…Oh? What are you all doing here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.6822794203,
      "endTime": 8.7023020987,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "ファンレター……読んでた……\n全国から、沢山届いてる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We've been reading… fan letters…\nwe've received a lot‚ from all over the country…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.9185379271,
      "endTime": 13.6618033652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "ひょっとして、この手紙の山、全部ファンレターなの？\n凄い量ね、普段の数倍はあるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ are all these mountains fan letters?\nThat's an incredible amount. It’s several times more than usual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.8780391936,
      "endTime": 23.2484060531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "これだけじゃない……\nメールやSNSからも、ファンの声が沢山届いてる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This isn't all…\nWe've received so many messages from fans through email and social media…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4646418814,
      "endTime": 29.8446418051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "この一つ一つが\n私達とファンが繋がった思い出なんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Each and every one of these\nis a memory of our connection with fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.0608776335,
      "endTime": 35.7784286741,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6072.4735575999985
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "この手紙は……沖縄で、一緒に釣りをした人から……\nあの時行った釣り場が、大変なことになってるって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This letter… is from the man we went fishing with in Okinawa…\nIt says the fishing spot we went to has become a big deal…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9946645025,
      "endTime": 46.0473853353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "そういえばネットニュースで見たわ。あの堤防に\nサニピのファンが連日詰めかけているそうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think I saw it on the internet news. Apparently‚ that breakwater\nhas been packed with Sunny Peace fans every day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.2636211637,
      "endTime": 53.0339819196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "堤防がファンの間で聖地になってる……\n私達と同じ場所で釣りをするファンが後を絶たない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The breakwater has become a sacred place for the fans…\nThere's a constant stream of fans fishing at the same spot as us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.250217748,
      "endTime": 61.383664250699994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "場所の問い合わせが、ひっきりなしにあるから……\n今では街の観光パンフレットでも紹介されてるって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since inquiries about the location are constantly coming in…\nit's even being featured in the town's tourist pamphlets…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.5999000791,
      "endTime": 70.0399004224,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12996.782410800002
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "聖地になってる場所なら他にもあるわよ。この手紙は\n私達が手伝いに行ったスーパーからだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's another place that's become a sacred place. This letter\nis from the supermarket where we helped out…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2561362508,
      "endTime": 79.6919184926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "あれからタイムセールにブリを売るのが恒例になって\nわざわざ県外から買いに来るファンもいるらしいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ever since then‚ selling yellowtail during the time sale has become a regular event‚\nand apparently some fans even come from other prefectures just to buy it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.8894695841,
      "endTime": 86.9221680247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "お店は大盛況で、店長もサニピの話題で\nお客さんと盛り上がっているそうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The shop is booming‚ and I heard the manager\nis enjoying chatting with customers about Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.1228029174,
      "endTime": 93.4878597182,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "大盛況で思い出したけど、お化け屋敷も\n私達が行ってから人気スポットになってるんだよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of booming businesses‚ the haunted house\nhas become a popular spot since we went there‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.6894695841,
      "endTime": 101.1235967241,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　私のアドバイスを取り入れたら\nより怖くなって、失神者続出って大人気なんだって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! Since they incorporated my advice\nit's become even scarier‚ so people are fainting left and right‚ and it's super popular!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.3228029174,
      "endTime": 109.88946932980001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8877.212905800008
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "お礼の手紙も来てたよ。今度、都内に二号店を出すから\nみんなで体験しに来てほしいって。ふふっ、楽しみだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They sent a thank you letter‚ too. They're opening a second branch in Tokyo‚\nand they want us all to come and experience it. Fufu‚ I'm looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.1057051582,
      "endTime": 120.9360682411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "失神者続出……ま、まぁ、行くかどうかは\n二号店が完成してから考えましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "People fainting left and right… W-well‚ we can decide\nwhether we go or not after the second branch opens.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.1523040695,
      "endTime": 130.6246854706,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "タレントスクールの子からも\nお礼の手紙が届いてたわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The girl at the talent school\nalso sent us a letter of thanks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.8189707362,
      "endTime": 134.9333431643,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4414.372428100023
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "スクールのみんなと「星見プロで新人オーディションが\n開催されたら絶対応募しようね」って話してるみたいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone at the school is saying‚ \"If Hoshimi Productions\nholds a newcomer audition‚ let's definitely apply!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.1055703723,
      "endTime": 143.54260288120003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "もしかしたら将来、あの子達の中から\n私達の後輩が生まれるかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Perhaps from among them‚\nour juniors might emerge in the future.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.7588387096,
      "endTime": 150.0625399196,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6641.186268899986
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "吹奏楽部の子達からも手紙が来てるよ\nあの時体育館にいた他の生徒からも沢山！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We also got letters from the high school brass band club‚\nand many from the other students who were in the gym that day!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.278775748,
      "endTime": 157.7065991008,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "全校生徒からファンレターをもらえるなんて\nなんだか凄いね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To receive fan letters from the entire student body…\nIt's kind of amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.9121090813,
      "endTime": 163.8356690331,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "サニピの歌と吹奏楽部の演奏が\nそれだけ多くの人の心に響いたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace's singing and the brass band's performance\nresonated with so many people's hearts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.0519048615,
      "endTime": 170.3222503586,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6581.436157000013
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10448.103030300019
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "これは、千紗ちゃんがダンスを教えた子から……\nこっちは、さくらちゃんが応援したソフトボール部……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This one is from the kid whom Chisa-chan taught to dance…\nAnd this one is from the softball club that Sakura-chan cheered for…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.538486187,
      "endTime": 178.3984861298,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11061.521498200022
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "私達が会いに行った人達から、こんなに沢山……\nあ、この手紙……北海道の病院で会った子からだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We got this many letters from the people we went to see…\nAh‚ this letter… It's from the girl we met at the hospital in Hokkaido…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.6147219582,
      "endTime": 188.4997563286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、本当！？　なんて書いてあるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ really!? What does it say?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.715992157,
      "endTime": 192.6739513798,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4317.348861500022
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "今度、大きな手術を受けることになったから……\nお医者さんにお願いして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She's going to have major surgery soon…\nSo she asked the doctor…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192.8826588237,
      "endTime": 199.3640872562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "手術中にサニピの曲を流してもらうって……\nそうすれば手術も怖くないから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…to play Sunny Peace songs during the surgery…\nThat way‚ she won't be scared of the surgery…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.5803230846,
      "endTime": 207.2403232181,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "大きな手術かぁ……うまくいくといいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A major surgery… I hope it goes well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 207.4565590465,
      "endTime": 212.3228403652,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5143.448638700022
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "手術が成功して元気になったら……今度は自分が\nアイドルになって、みんなを元気にしたい、って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She said if the surgery goes well and she fully recovers……\nshe wants to become an idol and cheer everyone up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.5232257132,
      "endTime": 220.8032257323,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "サニピみたいなアイドルになるのが……\n叶えたい、今の夢だって書いてある……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Becoming an idol like Sunny Peace…\nis her dream now‚ that's what she wrote…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 221.0194615607,
      "endTime": 227.59093544529998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "嬉しいわね。こうして見ると、ライブツアーを通して\n大勢の人と繋がれたって実感するわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That makes me happy. Looking at it like this‚ I realize that\nwe were able to connect with so many people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.8071712737,
      "endTime": 236.51088163900002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "行く先々で人が集まり過ぎて\n迷惑もかけちゃったよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Too many people gathered everywhere we went‚\nand we ended up causing trouble…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.7271174674,
      "endTime": 242.1464245086,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "あんなに人が集まるなんて私も予想外だったわ\nそれだけ私達が注目されてるってことなんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn't expect that many people to gather either.\nIt means that we're getting that much attention…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.3293351417,
      "endTime": 251.53425571969998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "サニピの人気を一番実感出来てなかったのは\n案外、私達自身だったのかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Perhaps the ones who haven't realized\nSunny Peace's popularity the most are actually us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 251.7293351417,
      "endTime": 259.39922154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "実感……そうかも……\n人の心は目に見えない……だから、実感しにくい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Realization… Maybe so…\nPeople's hearts are invisible… That's why it's hard to truly grasp…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.5960018083,
      "endTime": 269.7198562547,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "ツアータイトルを『繋ぐ』に決めた時……ファンと\n繋がったって実感出来るのか……不安もあった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we decided on \"Connect\" as the tour title… I was worried\nwhether I would be able to truly feel connected to the fans…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 269.9360920831,
      "endTime": 278.4853110238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk017.m4a",
      "text": "でも、全国を飛び回って……みんなの夢を聞いて……\n夢を叶えるお手伝いをして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ by traveling all over the country… by listening to everyone's dreams…\nby helping them achieve their dreams…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.8015529557,
      "endTime": 286.8115529938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk018.m4a",
      "text": "なんとなく……『繋ぐ』が分かった気がする……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel like… I understand what \"Connect\" means…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 287.0277888222,
      "endTime": 291.90878676610004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "分かる！　ステージで歌ってる時は\n客席のみんなと心が一つになった感じがしたよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know! When I was singing on stage‚\nit felt like my heart was becoming one with everyone in the audience!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 292.1250225945,
      "endTime": 299.295634739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "ツアーが終わった後も、こうして想いのこもった手紙を\n沢山もらえるなんて嬉しいよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's wonderful to receive a lot of heartfelt letters\nlike this‚ even after the tour is over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 299.4916892612,
      "endTime": 307.9492629612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "私達のしたことが、いろんな人に影響を与えて\n繋がって、広がっていったってことね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What we did was affecting various people‚\nconnecting and spreading.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 308.1654987896,
      "endTime": 315.79946695210003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "私達と繋がった人達が、みんな笑顔になって\n幸せになってくれたら最高だな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If the people we connected with are all smiling\nand feel happy‚ it will be the best～",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 315.9988321229,
      "endTime": 323.3469273492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "繋がったみんなを幸せにする……\nそれもアイドルの醍醐味かもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To bring happiness to everyone we've connected with…\nThat might be one of the real pleasures as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 323.5321654563,
      "endTime": 330.53586361460003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk019.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルは、みんなを笑顔にする……幸せにする……\nそれはきっと、巡り巡って自分自身も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Idols make everyone smile… make them happy…\nAnd that will surely‚ eventually come back to me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 330.752099443,
      "endTime": 341.6000424466,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk020.m4a",
      "text": "これが、繋がるということ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is what it means to be connected…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 342.15168469,
      "endTime": 345.6333757799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃん、なんだか凄く嬉しそう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan‚ you look really happy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 345.9125589614,
      "endTime": 350.0792255168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "今の雫ちゃん、とっても素敵な笑顔してるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You have such a lovely smile right now‚ Shizuku-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 350.2954613452,
      "endTime": 354.3613343005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk021.m4a",
      "text": "……うん、嬉しい\n私、みんなと繋がれて、幸せ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah‚ I'm happy.\nI'm happy to be connected with everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 354.5621280118,
      "endTime": 361.16212820249996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk022.m4a",
      "text": "私……アイドルになって、良かった……\nみんなと繋がれて、良かった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm… glad to be an idol…\nI'm glad‚ to be connected with everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 361.3783640309,
      "endTime": 370.1053478642,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}